DROP EXTERNAL TABLE DIM_Access;

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE DIM_Access (
	[ACCESS] nvarchar(4000),
	[USERID] nvarchar(4000),
	[USERTYPE] nvarchar(4000),
	[RESTRICTDIVISION] nvarchar(4000),
	[RESTRICTDEPOT] nvarchar(4000),
	[RESTRICTCOST] nvarchar(4000),
	[RESTRICTCOSTTYPE] nvarchar(4000)
	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'DataLake/Structured/Dimensions/DIM_ACCESS.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO


SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.DIM_Access
GO
